      "text": "How can speech datasets become reproducible, structured and privacy-first?",
      "suggestedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Capturing data is as important as training models. A useful speech workflow should preserve prompt, speaker, timing, quality, review and export context before any downstream model work begins.",
